snippet.title: Void Climber | Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Demo out now! Wishlist Void Climber on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2568730/Void_Climber/

Climb to the top of a collapsing universe in this parkour platformer with roguelike elements. Gather resources, spawn platforms, and obtain powerful upgrades to survive before the world crumbles beneath you. Just don’t fall into the void.
